    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Specialists in the study or science of theology, or religious doctrines and practices, generally from the viewpoint of religious believers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
